Upstream attribution
--------------------

rustyroute is based on and inspired by Eurostat's SeaRoute project:

    https://github.com/eurostat/searoute
    Maven coordinates: eu.europa.ec.eurostat:searoute-core
    Copyright (c) European Union, Eurostat
    Licensed under EUPL-1.2

Eurostat's SeaRoute maritime routing network (graph data derived from
shipping lanes and enriched with AIS data) and its shortest-path
algorithmic approach (Dijkstra over the maritime graph) inform this
project.

This repository does not vendor Eurostat graph data in the initial
skeleton. When upstream data or code is introduced in future commits,
this NOTICE will be updated to reflect the precise nature of the
derivative work, in line with EUPL-1.2 Article 5 (attribution rights).
